    "description": "《无极道人》玩家交流群：111758799<br><br>几十年前，江湖上曾有一场血雨腥风。 这飞炀殿烧杀抢掠，作恶多端，乃是江湖上第一大邪派。<br>殿主魔星武艺高强， 坐下更有八大高手为虎作伥。 前去讨伐的侠客们死伤惨重， 一时竟无人可挡。<br>直到忽然出现了，一个道人。<br><br>《无极道人》独创了全新的基于物理的角色运动系统，会随着玩家的操作，实时生成战斗和交互动画。<br>实时的战斗交互和流畅的打斗运动， 以呈现中国传统武术的独特之处。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/d2a4e626803c56e8105b5a68a9ffb9d3.poster.avif?t=1664766344\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/d2a4e626803c56e8105b5a68a9ffb9d3.webm?t=1664766344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/d2a4e626803c56e8105b5a68a9ffb9d3.mp4?t=1664766344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>参照现实的物理运动， 通过腿部的运动和各种力来计算角色的移动和平衡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/54f0ca4c1ffa69b0cb29abad39e93ce6.poster.avif?t=1664766344\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/54f0ca4c1ffa69b0cb29abad39e93ce6.webm?t=1664766344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/54f0ca4c1ffa69b0cb29abad39e93ce6.mp4?t=1664766344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每个运动都由物理进行模拟，受击的伤害和效果由相互之间的速度，惯性，受击角度等等参数来计算。<br>角色的运动会像真实世界中一样。 可以被拖拽，推搡，绊倒等等。<br>每次战斗计算的结果都是独特的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/c46ab730d506b9ee6c52c0ba16138b67.poster.avif?t=1664766344\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/c46ab730d506b9ee6c52c0ba16138b67.webm?t=1664766344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/c46ab730d506b9ee6c52c0ba16138b67.mp4?t=1664766344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/d8808ae97d4c8b1ce5c3aa007d40b3a1.poster.avif?t=1664766344\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/d8808ae97d4c8b1ce5c3aa007d40b3a1.webm?t=1664766344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/d8808ae97d4c8b1ce5c3aa007d40b3a1.mp4?t=1664766344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>还有各种武器可供选择。 每种类型的武器都会带来不同的战斗风格和感觉。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/8978a4bb99f22df09d2bed47c3b0bb48.poster.avif?t=1664766344\" width=480 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/8978a4bb99f22df09d2bed47c3b0bb48.webm?t=1664766344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872230/extras/8978a4bb99f22df09d2bed47c3b0bb48.mp4?t=1664766344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
